====Pokémon Legends: Z-A====
{{spoilers}}
Korrina is indirectly mentioned by [[AZ]] in a letter he wrote to the player after the credits of the game. In his letter, AZ revealed that prior to the game's events, Korrina had given away a Lucario to him in hopes that it might keep him safe. After AZ passes away, his Lucario and the letter are left in the player's room in [[Hotel Z]].

=====[[Mega Dimension]]=====
Korrina is called by [[Corbeau]] to [[Lumiose City]] to join [[Team MZ]] to help them solve the mysteries of [[Hyperspace Lumiose]].
{{endspoilers}}
